title: HENRY LEE CLAY
maintext: HENRY LEE CLAY, 71, of East Lynn, W.Va., died Nov. 1 at Cabell Huntington Hospital. Graveside service will be 11 a.m. Saturday at Ancil Clay Cemetery. Procession will leave 10:15 a.m. from Johnson Tiller Funeral Home.
